{
  "stem": "12674.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came there, my father and my brother were assigned to one of the buildings that used to be horse stables, where they had people live in these three, you know, wooden, three-layered-- three-level things on sacks of straw.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody had one narrow cot-like thing about the width of this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, 30 inches wide and 6 feet long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did the camp appear to you when you first arrived there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a very old place with wall-to-wall people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, there, there, there were 3,000 people living in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a little town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had moats, and a city wall, an underground thing, you know, passages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a fortress from 1600 something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maria Theresa was the empress from 1640 to 1680.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very-- they had a few people there-- 3,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then sometimes, there were 60,000 people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was wall-to-wall people and everybody-- a room like this would house maybe 30 people, with layers, you know, along there, and one across the end-- one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in Theresienstadt, I was assigned to, to work in something called the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- mica, which is a, a rock which splinters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's like, oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's, it's-- they use the, the isinglass, you know, the thing in front of, of a-- of kerosene stoves, those glass little things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That is stone, and that can be split.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they wanted it for aircraft insulation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a instrument, something like a nail file with a knife at the end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to split it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- we had little examples, so many micrometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
